  "title": "Service Crew / Cashier - Self-collection concept",
  "description": "<p><strong>Self-collection Service Crew / Cashier (Self-service Concept)</strong></p><p>Most orders will be done through online QR code self-ordering. The role will primarily be helping customers and passing food to them at the collection counter. </p><p>No prior experience needed. Full time and part time roles available.<br /></p><p><strong>Job Duties</strong></p><ul><li>Greet and assist customers</li><li>Show customers how to complete QR Code Ordering. Most orders will be done via QR self-ordering.</li><li>Handle POS (sales terminal), Food Delivery devices and all cashier transactions (where necessary)</li><li>Prepare and pack orders, buzz for customers and pass prepared food at collection counter.</li><li>Basic food/drink preparation.</li><li>Assist and support with stock replenishment</li><li>Coordination with Kitchen Team</li><li>Maintain food safety and hygiene standards</li><li>Adhere to SOPs/recipe guidelines</li><li>Assist where necessary, as assigned by the management.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>No prior experience needed, training will be provided</li><li>Salary will be based on experience</li><li>Familiarity with using iPads, food delivery devices and phones</li><li>Able to work efficiently in a fast-paced environment</li></ul><p><strong>Important Note:</strong></p><ul><li>We warmly welcome applications from individuals of all backgrounds, genders, religions and races.</li></ul>",
